{"id": 558, "genre": 1000, "title": "名人们是怎么评价中产阶级lifestyle的？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。好奇心研究所会不定期推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。", "record_count": 2593, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183622NA3rCBSvlUf1gZ9s.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-06T01:10:54Z", "questions": [{"id": 459, "title": "名人们是怎么评价中产阶级lifestyle的？", "content": "名人们是怎么评价中产阶级lifestyle的？ \r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 12932, "content": "毛姆：教养的唯一用途就是让人堂而皇之地说废话。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194004MwfaS08xzNiLhnqj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12934, "content": "鲁迅：爱人赠我百蝶巾，回她什么：猫头鹰。", "image": "img/option/option/201606071933394d9n281iWmhbeNz7.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12936, "content": "张爱玲：家中宝物也得拿出来让别人赏玩，然后自己才会重新发现它的价值。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193339qfXeUDv1pWHMOZk8.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12938, "content": "村上春树：每天早上都捏着鼻子喝奇腥无比的海豹油，再没效果岂能饶了它！", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193339urbN79L2mk0l6OUg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12940, "content": "村上春树：在过午的酒吧里用熊本牡蛎佐酒，啜饮冰镇夏布利白葡萄酒。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193731o4mKIXlUGTg9y3js.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12941, "content": "王尔德：只有无聊的人才会把早餐吃出花样来。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182812vwAXHyRThC5IEcPo.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12942, "content": "王尔德：时尚总是丑得难以容忍，所以每隔六个月我们都只好改一次。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193339WOtGuVSBIpFgHPMk.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 12943, "content": "福楼拜：大自然多美啊！——每到乡下，必作此语。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182556AON9idksfChmKMJX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}